02:43.697 --> 02:49.636 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Lynch pointed to
a new FBI
report showing a 67 percent
increase in hate

02:49.669 --> 02:52.973 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
