lost nearly
36 points to close under 18868.

04:43.016 --> 04:47.921 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Nasdaq fell 12, and the S&amp;P
500 slipped
five.

04:47.954 --> 04:52.959 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
