22:25.344 --> 22:30.416 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Now those young adults are
uncertain and anxious
about what's to come.

22:30.449 --> 22:33.986 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Jeffrey Brown has the story.

22:34.019 --> 22:37.590 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I was 11 years old when I
immigrated to the
United States.

22:37.623 --> 22:39.925 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I didn't know what being
undocumented was.

22:39.959 --> 22:44.029 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I didn't even know that a piece
of paper can
actually determine my whole
future.

22:44.063 --> 22:47.600 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DIANA CHACON, College Student: I
thought that
working really hard throughout
high school

22:47.633 --> 22:51.704 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
would give me the same
opportunities that
most have, ones that graduated.

22:51.737 --> 22:56.342 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Like, you can go apply to any
college you
want, go study upstate.

22:56.375 --> 23:01.313 align:left position:25%,start line:73.33% size:75%
JEFFREY BROWN:
Twenty-one-year-old Diana Chacon
has come a long way from her
birth in Lima,

23:01.347 --> 23:02.848 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
