25:47.913 --> 25:51.683 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
His own uncertain future, he
says, now informs
his work and activism.

25:51.717 --> 25:54.186 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, if DACA is repealed, what
would happen?

25:54.219 --> 25:56.555 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
CARLOS VARGAS, Immigrant
Activist: I don't
know.

25:56.588 --> 25:57.756 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And that's the scary part.

25:57.790 --> 25:59.658 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It's a little bit frightening.

25:59.691 --> 26:00.826 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
But we're going to fight.

26:00.859 --> 26:01.960 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
