26:01.994 --> 26:03.429 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If they do take it away, we
demand something
better.

26:03.462 --> 26:05.063 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: But what does
that mean?

26:05.097 --> 26:06.465 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I mean, what would you do?

26:06.498 --> 26:08.267 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
CARLOS VARGAS: Go out.

26:08.300 --> 26:12.871 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
