26:19.678 --> 26:21.447 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I'm going to give you DACA.

26:21.480 --> 26:22.514 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
We fought for it.

26:22.548 --> 26:23.682 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
There was a lot of civil
disobedience.

26:23.715 --> 26:26.084 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
There was a lot of organizing.

26:26.118 --> 26:29.855 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I think that just means
we're going to
do that to a bigger scale now.

26:29.888 --> 26:35.994 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Staten Island is
home to a
fast-growing immigrant
community, many, like

26:36.028 --> 26:38.297 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
