immigrant
from Eastern Europe.

26:52.611 --> 26:54.880 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SEBASTIAN DEMETRIO, Trump
Supporter: I came
here legal.

26:54.913 --> 26:55.981 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
