27:14.833 --> 27:18.203 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Staten Island
City Councilman
Joe Borelli served as a
co-chairman for the

27:18.237 --> 27:20.138 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
