27:20.172 --> 27:21.607 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOSEPH BORELLI, Co-Chair, Donald
Trump New
York Campaign: It's the
sentiment that we

27:21.640 --> 27:23.175 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
