place where many
immigrants come to.

27:26.879 --> 27:31.183 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Of course, New York is broadly
the home of
immigration to this country.

27:31.216 --> 27:35.721 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The majority of people who come
to New York
as immigrants come here through
a legal process,

27:35.754 --> 27:38.156 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
