ancestors did through
Ellis Island.

27:38.190 --> 27:41.927 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Fifty percent of our small
businesses here
in New York City are owned by
immigrants or

27:41.960 --> 27:44.396 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
