combination thereof.

27:44.429 --> 27:46.131 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
They are making New York great.

27:46.164 --> 27:47.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And they are making America
great.

27:47.866 --> 27:49.935 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
As long as you follow the rules,
you should
be welcome here.

27:49.968 --> 27:53.405 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: His message to
constituents
fearing deportation now?

27:53.438 --> 27:55.440 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOSEPH BORELLI: I would tell
these people
to relax slightly.

27:55.474 --> 27:57.476 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And I understand it's
concerning.

27:57.509 --> 27:59.311 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But they should wait to see what
the administration
puts forth.

27:59.344 --> 28:01.013 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: We're getting them
out of our
country.

28:01.046 --> 28:02.948 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
