28:02.981 --> 28:06.618 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: In his first
televised interview
as president-elect, Mr. Trump
pledged to focus

28:06.652 --> 28:10.155 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
