47:31.115 --> 47:32.850 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: A footnote to this
story.

47:32.883 --> 47:36.687 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ROBERT MACNEIL: I feel that the
outpouring
of sympathy for her too-young
