upside down,

47:46.297 --> 47:51.535 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
that she provides an emotional
outlet for
people who prize the diversity
of American

47:51.569 --> 48:00.511 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
society and, in her career, a
symbol of the
values they want to hold on to.

48:00.544 --> 48:06.417 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANNE DAVENPORT: What Gwen taught
me was grit,
grace and gratitude, what I call
the three

48:06.450 --> 48:08.219 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
G's.

48:08.252 --> 48:13.224 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
