call, she chose
happy.

48:16.894 --> 48:21.599 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: This is an amazing
place, chockful
of the expected and the
unexpected.

48:21.632 --> 48:26.437 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANNE DAVENPORT: She always saw
the bright
spot, even when she wasn't
feeling well towards

48:26.470 --> 48:27.438 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
the end.

48:27.471 --> 48:29.306 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: I love it.

48:29.340 --> 48:31.609 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANNE DAVENPORT: And also a kind
of fun lesson,
on the road, whether it was the
New Hampshire

48:31.642 --> 48:34.912 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
