and Twizzlers.

48:34.945 --> 48:38.649 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARGE HUBBARD: Gwen taught me,
put hot sauce
on my eggs.

48:38.682 --> 48:40.851 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
EMILY CARPEAUX: Gwen taught me
