giving that up as she battled
her illness

49:00.304 --> 49:02.072 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
in the last weeks.

49:02.106 --> 49:08.512 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We will also remember Gwen for
that beautiful
wide smile, along with her
devotion to high

49:08.546 --> 49:12.950 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
standards of journalism, made
