colleague and friend.

49:12.983 --> 49:15.886 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Part of what
Gwen taught
me -- and this was from watching
her at the

49:15.920 --> 49:20.391 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
