high rate of
HIV among black women in
America.

49:24.595 --> 49:29.600 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: What should the
government's role
be in helping to end the growth
of this epidemic?

49:29.633 --> 49:32.670 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Neither of
them had any
idea what she was talking about.

49:32.703 --> 49:38.042 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And what Gwen taught me in that
moment was
that bringing uncomfortable
truths and facts

49:38.075 --> 49:40.878 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
