journalist is
supposed to do.

49:40.911 --> 49:46.183 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
P.J. TOBIA: Gwen taught me that
you can always
find some kind of diversity, a
woman or a

49:46.217 --> 49:50.988 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
