her.

50:11.775 --> 50:14.411 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SARA JUST: Gwen was a huge fan
of the show
"Hamilton."

50:14.445 --> 50:17.581 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
