50:23.654 --> 50:27.925 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There's a huge, gaping hole in
our newsroom
and in the industry of
journalism in general

50:27.958 --> 50:29.293 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
without Gwen.

50:29.326 --> 50:30.327 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
She was one of a kind.

50:30.361 --> 50:33.397 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But she also planted a lot of
seeds.

50:33.430 --> 50:37.134 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
She was a mentor, a guide, a
friend to a whole
slew of younger journalists.

50:37.167 --> 50:41.672 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
She made time in her busy
schedule to offer
advice, be a sounding board, a
cheerleader,

50:41.705 --> 50:42.806 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
an ally.

50:42.840 --> 50:44.508 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ELIZABETH SUMMERS: Gwen taught
